# L4 - Early Birds and Night Owls

## Vocabulary

- Morning person
- Late riser.
- Power napper. It's a person who needs a little nap (sleeping short period) to feeling right.
- Night owl.

## Grammar - Reduced time clauses

> Page: 29

`Clase: Subject + Verb`

Means you will elminiate something

### Examples

- I like to listen to electronic music while I study -> I like to listen to electronic music while *studying*.
- After *I graduate*, I'll become a school teacher -> After *graduating*, I'll become a school teacher

    > After, before and while are adverbo of time.


